(1) Gorgeous Stainless Crowned Target Barrel
 
We start with a USA Made 18" Fluted HBAR Barrel with a mid-length gas system.
 
The threading is removed, taking the barrel down to ~17".  From here, the surface is squared, prepped, and then an 11 degree crown is carefully cut into the metal.  The outside ridge then chamfer cut and sanded for an elegant smoothness.
 
After crowning, the surface is hand polished to a near mirror finish. 
 
The end result is a stunning, fluted, crowned HBAR barrel.
